# {{SITE_TITLE}} — Cursor Rules

## Tech stack

- Jekyll static site with zer0-mistakes theme
- Bootstrap 5 for styling
- Liquid templating
- Docker for development

## Key paths

- `pages/_posts/` — blog posts (layout: article)
- `pages/_docs/` — documentation
- `_layouts/` — page layouts
- `_includes/` — reusable components
- `_sass/` — custom styles
- `_data/` — site data (navigation, authors, etc.)

## Commands

```bash
docker compose up              # dev server
bundle exec jekyll build       # build
```

## Rules

- Match existing Liquid/HTML style
- Mobile-first Bootstrap 5 components
- Front matter required on all content files
